tasks.task: Set up a rooftop solar panel system.
subtasks: Measure and prepare the roof for solar panel installations.
Install rails for mounting solar panels.
Mount solar panels using fasteners and spacers.
Connect microinverters and daisy-chain the AC wires.
Install junction boxes and conduit for wiring.
Mount the combiner box and connect strings.
Protect wiring with clips to prevent damage.
Install AC disconnect and performance meter.
